						<div class="postbody">A DMC IRQ, as I recall, is rather imprecise and carries a margin of error too great for PPU-related timing.  You can use the IRQ, but unless you follow it up with a sprite 0 hit, the bottom of the screen will show some flickering due to the large margin of error.
<br />
<br />Is there any reason why you cannot port your code to MMC3?</div>

